<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2164] debian build dep on ant-optional is missing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2164</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Without the ant-optional package installed in Debian, builds fail (on lenny) with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Could not create type regexpmapper due to No supported regular expression matcher found: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.apache.tools.ant.util.regexp.Jdk14RegexpMatcher&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached patch makes it build. Tested on lenny and squeeze.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
